87451, "create_time": 1657503358, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "刚性兑付的支撑是什么呢？", "timestamp": 1657503358}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287458, "create_time": 1657503595, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 寻思没否认过啊，懂了啥😅", "timestamp": 1657503595}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287460, "create_time": 1657503702, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 利率代价，国内银行都是通过市场地位进行的低吸高贷。同时走的国家信用背书的牌照经济，并非完整的商业银行体系。刚性兑付已经是多年的传统了。这里牵扯的问题就是利率，这个利率定价和风险是否匹配，取决于募集资金投向是否合规。风险计算是否合理。这里牵扯的责任就是地方政府和地方的银保监会。", "timestamp": 1657503702}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287463, "create_time": 1657503787, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 所以并非是储户买了什么产品，而是储户认为是什么产品，实际的银行柜台很乱，有很多诱导消费的情况。所以最直接的判定方法就是通过利率。利率和风险挂钩，银行的准备金率是否备足。所以怎么算，在中国的制度下，都算不到储户。", "timestamp": 1657503787}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287468, "create_time": 1657503853, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 既然监管并非是 民营企业自发形成的组织与政府合作，类似美联储雏形和各种行业协会。主要由政府主导的，那么政府就要承担责任。从地方上升到中央。", "timestamp": 1657503853}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287469, "create_time": 1657503869, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 其实我是想表达，支撑某一银行实现刚性兑付的资金应该由谁来负责呢？", "timestamp": 1657503869}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287470, "create_time": 1657503871, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Carol: 你爱啥啥，你要反驳就反驳。 不用扯其他的。", "timestamp": 1657503871}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287473, "create_time": 1657503929, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 财政，从所有权归属上，政府不应当等同于法人，应当承担无限责任，因为银行的信用由政府背书，应当由政府赔偿。", "timestamp": 1657503929}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287476, "create_time": 1657504001, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 可以用地方政府的资产作为抵押，从国有银行贷款赔偿。", "timestamp": 1657504001}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287478, "create_time": 1657504021, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以银行应该成为政府的一个组成部门？", "timestamp": 1657504021}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287479, "create_time": 1657504041, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 没反驳您的科普呢", "timestamp": 1657504041}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287481, "create_time": 1657504057, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re 洞主: 也没让您看看其他的", "timestamp": 1657504057}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287483, "create_time": 1657504188, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 取决于你说的那种银行。现在很多银行走的是“股份制商业银行”。非国资的部分有很多都是与政府有关的利益相关方。属于制度作恶。", "timestamp": 1657504188}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287489, "create_time": 1657504267, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以一个好的制度，应该关掉非国资的银行？其余的银行，应该由政府保证刚性兑付？", "timestamp": 1657504267}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287492, "create_time": 1657504298, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 但是从实际表现上，储户利率十分低，完全符合垄断情况，也就是大部分利率被银行拿走。这里涉及到牌照经济。银行并非市场竞争越大越好，这里又涉及个人绩效和企业利益的委托代理问题。至于应该是否属于政府部门，我对行政不了解，但是所有权上应当属于政府。从垄断结果来看。", "timestamp": 1657504298}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287493, "create_time": 1657504312, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 已经回答。", "timestamp": 1657504312}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287494, "create_time": 1657504344, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 可以结合我国的影子银行情况来看，以及P2P的兴起。", "timestamp": 1657504344}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287495, "create_time": 1657504390, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 所以你怎么说，这次都是政府问题，它必须为自己的拍照经济买单，因为你是监管方承担监管责任。何况这里有很大的银行管理问题。", "timestamp": 1657504390}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287497, "create_time": 1657504426, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以你认为，银行的所有权应该属于政府？而对于那些所有权不属于政府的银行，都应该关停？", "timestamp": 1657504426}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287500, "create_time": 1657504536, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: Re Eve: 是什么样的流动性管理，能让最开始几个储户取钱变成挤兑。 2022年了，不是08年了。", "timestamp": 1657504536}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287504, "create_time": 1657504651, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 没有这种推论，谢谢，我只说政府经营牌照经济，实际上就承担了监管责任，何况这个银行大股东是，许昌农村商业银行和新郑商业银行。", "timestamp": 1657504651}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287505, "create_time": 1657504734, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 我的论点，在最开始的标题。不用诱导扭曲。我说过银行不需要过度竞争，不代表我要求关停。地方银行本来是放了不发达地区被发达地区吸血而设立。这是经管常识。所以我不可能同意这种愚蠢的观点。", "timestamp": 1657504734}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287506, "create_time": 1657504743, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 5, "text": "Re 洞主: 或者我这么问，你是否支持非政府所有的商业银行可以在中国运营？", "timestamp": 1657504743}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287513, "create_time": 1657505071, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 符合巴塞尔协议的就可以。", "timestamp": 1657505071}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 287514, "create_time": 1657505145, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 但是结合我国特殊情况，可能还需要专门设立一些地方银行，否则地方没有资金发展。", "timestamp": 1657505145}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 289149, "create_time": 1657560233, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "你说的牌照经济也好、非市场化利率也好，都对，但金融的实际运行不是你想的这么简单，不可能但凡接近市场利率的银行业务就全给你归到存款里，隐性“刚性兑付”不知道吗？别老扯啥一言堂，管所有的政府是应该负全责，但很明显从来也没负全责过，这就是中国特色市场经济，这并不是可以一锤子敲死的负面问题", "timestamp": 1657560233}], "create_time": 1657501413, "cw": null, "hot_score": null, "is_blocked": false, "is_reported": null, "is_tmp": false, "last_comment_time": 1657560233, "likenum": 11, "n_attentions": 11, "n_comments": 42, "pid": 81299, "poll": null, "reply": 42, "text": "#81296\n你想科普什么？你想说什么？\n我只说一句话 只要是在你村镇银行办理业务，只要你是牌照经济不是商业银行体系，只要利率合理，你就得刚性兑付！懂？\n\n不用说具体哪个账户没有意义！你存款的时候录音了么？存单有写募集资金投降么？这么点利率能把本金赔光？你当树洞没有经管学生？", "timestamp": 1657501413}}